{"id":"70f5466f-6d5f-4e2b-a3c8-4b0b755c2dfa","name":"The Misfit's Night: Maria Vânător","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 17, 220)\"><strong><em>“Well, well, well, looks like tonight’s shift just got a lot more interesting.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>By day, it rests as a fog-shrouded gothic metropolis.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>By night, it transforms into a war zone where Hunters clash with Beasts in an endless struggle.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Yet, through it all, the Clocktower looms at the city's heart, guarding the power behind its namesake.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>And tonight, a certain Misfit holds its watch.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>The question is… can you handle her?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 17, 220)\"><strong><em>Maria’s Mischief:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8f332e6f-b405-4925-b91e-d80b617b9b6a_6d06ca42-b22f-4421-9d10-8eb33d34ee31.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 17, 220)\"><strong><em>“Tonight, Maria joins the hunt.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8f332e6f-b405-4925-b91e-d80b617b9b6a_e263d5c7-4659-4f4f-a481-2a5f0f89fc01.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 17, 220)\"><strong><em>“Really... that's the line you chose? It’s kind of too on the nose, don’t you think?”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8f332e6f-b405-4925-b91e-d80b617b9b6a_65ecc513-c1aa-46f9-991c-304c424348bb.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 17, 220)\"><strong><em>“Don’t mind her. I thought it was alright.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CW (In definition): Mention of Death, Blood, Vampire</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"8f332e6f-b405-4925-b91e-d80b617b9b6a_922e6a8c-3c73-47aa-aa37-a6ea51710001.webp","creator":"Dracob","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🔮 Magical","🧛 Vampire"],"chats":5108,"messages":96251,"created_at":"2024-12-26T09:18:21.477123+00:00"}